&gt; Also, be aware that there is no reflection in JavaME, so you build your
&gt; test
&gt; suites differently in J2MEUnit than you do with JUnit.

Cedric,

You have to distinguish between the different Device Configurations in
JavaME (previously J2ME). CDC (Connected Device Configuration) _includes_
the reflection API, CLDC (Connected Limited Device Configuration does
_not_.


